6
00:00:22,585 --> 00:00:26,705
After following this video, you will know
the basic mechanisms that bind quarks and

7
00:00:26,705 --> 00:00:31,330
antiquarks to form mesons, and
their excited states and their spectra,

8
00:00:31,330 --> 00:00:35,520
